{"tid":334550,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"AIRBNB一問","createTime":"2017-07-24T21:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T10:18:39.000Z","uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ccf883590dfc5c8215f4e3005fbec06e73d776","tid":334550,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T21:30:28.000Z","msg":"以前未BOOK過AIRBNB  今次去旅行第一次BOOK<br />\n我上網用信用卡比完錢 AIRBNB個網都寫 確認左  但係搵個房東 佢就無應機<br />\n然後過左幾日啦 信用卡都仲未扣我數  <br />\n我上網睇話係要個房東 接受左 先會扣數(好似係?)<br />\n咁我依加個情況 係唔係有可能 個房東可能無睇到/無理到/人不在 咁上下?<br />\n<br />\n我係咪可以同AIRBNB 全數退返錢(事實上都未收錢) 然後重新BOOK過?(距離入住日子約10日)"},{"pid":"1ede1f0019552bc61defd5e5a81a747e8511884a","tid":334550,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:47:51.000Z","msg":"你個情況應該係request booking,要等房東ACCEPT左先會扣錢."},{"pid":"b93177176121dcca55e8d1f1d042d6c52bf680f6","tid":334550,"uid":17104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:47:18.000Z","msg":"你要等host確認左先得<br />\n一開始你禁俾錢個啲唔算確認左<br />\n要inbox入面有呢句先得<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/194559_d6133c012b12091074de2a18120fb0de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F194559_d6133c012b12091074de2a18120fb0de.jpg&h=40389352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔知2日內唔確認就會自動cancel你個request 當你無book過<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/194643_6b6057f9385b5c3e81ac0490709dee79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F194643_6b6057f9385b5c3e81ac0490709dee79.jpg&h=ee0ce8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就好似咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我禁左好多次佢都唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想煩可以搵個啲有閃電既=即時確認<br />\n咁就唔洗等佢覆你"},{"pid":"64fb989fbe1c158820a29cc23186694267dc3ca8","tid":334550,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要等host確認左先得<br />\n一開始你禁俾錢個啲唔算確認左<br />\n要inbox入面有呢句先得<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/194559_d6133c012b12091074de2a18120fb0de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F194559_d6133c012b12091074de2a18120fb0de.jpg&h=40389352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔知2日內唔確認就會自動cancel你個request 當你無book過<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/194643_6b6057f9385b5c3e81ac0490709dee79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F194643_6b6057f9385b5c3e81ac0490709dee79.jpg&h=ee0ce8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就好似咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我禁左好多次佢都唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想煩可以搵個啲有閃電既=即時確認<br />\n咁就唔洗等佢覆你</blockquote><br />\n好詳盡 明曬 唔該曬巴打<br />\n祝你都book到房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aacbb384323206f335d730050279a1531f28059","tid":334550,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"巴打 <br />\n<br />\n$250 link  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.airbnb.com.hk/c/jor12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.airbnb.com.hk%2Fc%2Fjor12&d=Eg2fUXOi9IVgHGyzkiocPG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=440f2d6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.airbnb.com.hk/c/jor12</a>"}]}